diff --git a/CHANGELOG.d/fix_vtas-wildcard-inferred.md b/CHANGELOG.d/fix_vtas-wildcard-inferred.md
new file mode 100644
index 00000000..98899b51
--- /dev/null
+++ b/CHANGELOG.d/fix_vtas-wildcard-inferred.md
@@ -0,0 +1,12 @@
+* Stop emitting warnings for wildcards in Visible Type Applications
+
+  Previously, the below usage of a wildcard (i.e. `_`) would
+  incorrectly cause the compiler to emit a warning.
+  
+  ```purs
+  f :: forall @a. a -> a
+  f = identity
+
+  x :: { x :: Int }
+  x = f @{ x :: _ } { x: 42 }
+  ```
